tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE earthquake_epicenters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    latitude DECIMAL,
    longitude DECIMAL,
    magnitude DECIMAL,
    date_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE epicenters (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  latitude FLOAT,
  longitude FLOAT,
  magnitude FLOAT,
  date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE earthquakes (
  event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  epicenter_id INT REFERENCES epicenters(id),
  region_id INT REFERENCES regions(region_id),
  depth FLOAT,
  type VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE EarthquakeLocations (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   latitude FLOAT,
   longitude FLOAT,
   magnitude FLOAT,
   depth FLOAT
)
